THEMBISA MDODA is back on the small screen.Thembisa, who presented Our Perfect Wedding, has made a great comeback!Sunday Sun can reveal that the reality TV host has taken back the reins from Jessica Nkosi.Sources close to the situation claim that producers of the show got sick and tired of Jessica&rsquo;s diva tendencies and demands.One source, who spoke on condition of anonymity, told Sunday Sun Jessica would often delay production &ndash; and was lacking in people skills.&ldquo;She would delay production and sometimes not rock up because she was over-committed,&rdquo; said the source.According to this informant, the production team also complained about Jessica.Our mole also said that even some of the contestants complained about the manner in which Jessica treated them.&ldquo;She would sometimes shout and yell at some of the contestants, especially when things didn&rsquo;t go her way,&rdquo; claimed the showbiz mole.Another source alleged that producers decided to bring Thembisa back because she was good at handling people.&ldquo;Thembisa is no diva. She&rsquo;s chilled and takes her brief,&rdquo; said the source.The TV mole went on to say Thembisa has people skills, and gets along well with people from all walks of life.&ldquo;She&rsquo;s not perfect, but nice to work with. And she&rsquo;s way better than Jessica, and people love her,&rdquo; said the source.When called for a comment, Jessica requested the SunTeam to call her after 10 minutes, but she hung up on us. Mzansi Magic&rsquo;s publicity manager Bongiwe Potelwa-Metsing said: &ldquo;I can confirm that Thembisa is coming back. She was given time off because she was exhausted. It&rsquo;s also because the audience likes her too.&rdquo;Thembisa could not be reached for comment and she failed to respond to our SMSes.